---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — MinimalDev"
  description="About MinimalDev: free online utility tools built for speed and clarity."
  canonicalPath="/legal/about/"
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">About MinimalDev</h1>

    <section class="section">
      <p class="lead">
        MinimalDev is a lightweight collection of free online utility tools—calculators, converters, and quick helpers—built to be fast, mobile-first, and easy to use.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>One tool per page</strong> so it’s easy to bookmark and share.</li>
        <li><strong>Simple UX</strong> with clear inputs and readable results.</li>
        <li><strong>Performance-first</strong> design with minimal scripts.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>How the site works</h2>
      <p class="note">
        Most tools run in your browser. We do not require accounts or logins and we avoid unnecessary data collection.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p class="note">
        Suggestions or issues? Please reach out via the <a href="/legal/contact/">Contact</a> page.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>